     H            Y.
     F** UEXR05B *******************************************
     F*  EXSUB - GET TABLE# OF AAMPP11 FROM SHIN/DEPT      *
     F*  J. WATANABE  2023.08.10                           *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR05B'
     F*                    PARM           P@SHN  12
     F*                    PARM           P@DPT   4
     F*                    PARM           P@DAT   8
     F*                    PARM           O@##    2
     F*                    PARM           O@TYP   1
     F*  IN  P@SHN  12   IAF PART#
     F*  "   P@DPT   4   DEPT
     F*  "   P@DAT   8   DATE   (BLANK=TODAY)
     F*  OUT O@##    2   TABLE#
     F*  "   O@TYP   1   KANBAN TYPE
     F******************************************************
     FAAMPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     E                    KO         15  3               NEW PROCESS
     E                    BM         15  4 0             NEW DEPT
     E                    KB         15  3               NEW MACHINE
     E                    NB         15  6               NEW LOCATION
     E                    TY         15  1               NEW TYPE
     E                    HB         15 12               NEW PART#
      *
     E                    QK         15  3               OLD PROCESS
     E                    QB         15  4 0             OLD DEPT
     E                    QN         15  3               OLD MACHINE
     E                    QT         15  6               OLD LOCATION
     E                    QS         15  1               OLD TYPE
     E                    QH         15 12               OLD PART#
      *
     E                    KHZ        15 10 0             CHANGE DATE
